title: NFL ATL: Week 16 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 16 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling,  and Kevin Patra -- recap all of the Week 16 action including the blowout “Sunday Night Football” matchup between the Chicago Bears and Philadelphia Eagles. Don’t miss the key takeaways and analysis from each game. Also, help the heroes by nominating them for the 2013 Stitcher Awards at stitcher.promotw.com. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
